01:10:28,558 --> 01:10:31,117
<i>'Flowers... and cash. '</i>

501
01:10:39,769 --> 01:10:42,431
<i>He's asking for a last cigarette.</i>

502
01:10:50,047 --> 01:10:52,015
<i>Non smoking</i>

503
01:12:27,783 --> 01:12:29,614
What's he doing?

504
01:12:33,855 --> 01:12:35,323
He's praying.

505
01:12:58,682 --> 01:13:00,047
Execute.

506
01:13:58,980 --> 01:14:00,241
Dead.

507
01:14:10,457 --> 01:14:12,221
- It's over.
- Yes.

508
01:14:13,761 --> 01:14:15,126
It's over.

509
01:15:06,584 --> 01:15:10,043
<i>The sky has grown old.</i>

510
01:15:28,974 --> 01:15:30,533
He's gone!

511
01:15:44,891 --> 01:15:49,051
<i>Coming soon:
the adventures of Mr. Merde in NY</i>

512
01:15:54,667 --> 01:15:58,331
<i>Directed by Leos Carax</i>

513
01:16:42,184 --> 01:16:46,348
<i>How long will it take
before this circle disappears?</i>

514
01:16:48,592 --> 01:16:51,959
<i>10 seconds, 10 minutes,</i>

515
01:16:52,095 --> 01:16:55,259
<i>10 hours, 10 days,</i>

516
01:16:55,399 --> 01:16:58,425
<i>10 months, 10 years...</i>

517
01:17:01,372 --> 01:17:04,829
<i>I've been living in this house
for 10 years.</i>

518
01:17:07,378 --> 01:17:09,700
<i>I am a hikikomori.</i>

519
01:17:20,592 --> 01:17:24,961
<i>Usually, hikikomoris live
at the expense of their parents.</i>

520
01:17:25,097 --> 01:17:27,964
<i>But I live alone.</i>

521
01:17:29,101 --> 01:17:31,536
<i>Defecating with the door open,
I don't care.</i>

522
01:17:31,670 --> 01:17:33,934
<i>Falling asleep while defecating,</i>

523
01:17:34,072 --> 01:17:35,835
<i>I don't care.</i>

524
01:17:38,177 --> 01:17:42,443
<i>Strangely,
I don't watch television.</i>

525
01:17:43,283 --> 01:17:45,547
<i>When was the last time
I watched it?</i>

526
01:17:48,989 --> 01:17:52,355
<i>However,
I feed myself every day.</i>

527
01:17:53,393 --> 01:17:55,157
<i>I don't need a table.</i>

528
01:17:59,199 --> 01:18:03,135
<i>Those who are sensitive
would have noticed,</i>

529
01:18:03,671 --> 01:18:07,374
<i>but my own way of tidying up,
practiced for 10 years</i>

530
01:18:07,375 --> 01:18:10,344
<i>has now reached
the level of art.</i>

531
01:18:15,082 --> 01:18:17,244
<i>It's hard to believe,</i>

532
01:18:18,286 --> 01:18:21,551
<i>but I have read all these books.</i>

533
01:18:24,893 --> 01:18:31,662
<i>Lately, reading magazines about
climbing, fishing and travelling</i>

534
01:18:32,401 --> 01:18:34,369
<i>suddenly makes me miss home.</i>

535
01:18:38,074 --> 01:18:42,443
<i>I never get into the room
that my father used.</i>

536
01:18:44,280 --> 01:18:46,943
<i>The envelope of money
my father sends.</i>

537
01:18:47,083 --> 01:18:48,745
<i>I open it every month.</i>

538
01:18:49,886 --> 01:18:54,255
<i>The first year
money came with a letter.</i>

539
01:18:54,992 --> 01:18:56,755
<i>For the next 9 years</i>

540
01:18:57,894 --> 01:18:59,555
<i>only money.</i>

541
01:19:01,898 --> 01:19:04,060
<i>Brand new crisp banknotes.</i>

542
01:19:05,802 --> 01:19:07,361
<i>How exciting.</i>

543
01:19:09,107 --> 01:19:12,543
<i>With money and a telephone,
everything is OK</i>

544
01:19:12,678 --> 01:19:14,646
<i>as everything
can be delivered.</i>

545
01:19:15,781 --> 01:19:18,442
<i>The bell is ringing. I open the door.</i>

546
01:19:18,584 --> 01:19:20,848
<i>I take. I give.</i>

547
01:19:20,986 --> 01:19:22,247
<i>I close the door.</i>

548
01:19:24,089 --> 01:19:26,956
<i>With the delivery men.</i>

549
01:19:27,092 --> 01:19:29,754
<i>I never make eye contact.</i>

550
01:19:32,998 --> 01:19:36,162
<i>On Saturdays, I always order a pizza.</i>

551
01:19:36,602 --> 01:19:39,765
So you never look at
people's faces?

552
01:19:39,905 --> 01:19:40,964
<i>Right.</i>

553
01:19:43,476 --> 01:19:46,036
<i>I hated having contact
with people.</i>

554
01:19:52,585 --> 01:19:55,749
<i>I hated having contact
with the sunlight too.</i>

555
01:20:07,402 --> 01:20:10,564
<i>I like watching the sunlight.</i>

556
01:20:15,410 --> 01:20:17,178
<i>I can see it...</i>

557
01:20:17,179 --> 01:20:18,646
<i>The movement of the sunlight.</i>

558
01:20:29,391 --> 01:20:31,952
<i>Others may not</i>

559
01:20:33,696 --> 01:20:37,257
<i>but I can even see
the hour hand moving.</i>

560
01:20:44,107 --> 01:20:46,372
<i>Everything is moving.</i>

561
01:20:52,683 --> 01:21:00,454
<i>It has been 10 years
since I last moved.</i>

562
01:21:19,110 --> 01:21:21,271
<i>It has been 11 years</i>

563
01:21:22,113 --> 01:21:24,344
<i>living in the house.</i>

564
01:21:32,491 --> 01:21:34,254
<i>Strictly speaking.</i>

565
01:21:36,295 --> 01:21:37,853
<i>I am a hikikomori.</i>

566
01:21:41,801 --> 01:21:44,861
<i>I digest better.</i>

567
01:21:48,108 --> 01:21:49,871
<i>When I fall asleep
on the toilet</i>

568
01:21:50,010 --> 01:21:51,477
<i>I have sweet dreams.</i>

569
01:21:55,716 --> 01:21:57,945
<i>The reading continues.</i>

570
01:22:02,088 --> 01:22:03,750
<i>The smell of my father...</i>

571
01:22:07,495 --> 01:22:09,053
<i>Saturday is pizza day.</i>

572
01:22:12,500 --> 01:22:16,164
<i>With the delivery men,
I don't make any...</i>

573
01:22:26,114 --> 01:22:28,275
<i>The first eye contact in 11 years.</i>

574
01:24:21,103 --> 01:24:22,263
Excuse me...

575
01:25:38,918 --> 01:25:40,180
Buttons?

576
01:25:56,904 --> 01:25:59,668
C, o, m...

577
01:26:02,509 --> 01:26:05,569
Coma.

578
01:26:33,739 --> 01:26:35,776
Did you push it?

579
01:26:38,914 --> 01:26:41,280
- Yes.
- You did?

580
01:27:25,230 --> 01:27:26,998
There's a mistake.

581
01:27:30,302 --> 01:27:32,868
The eighth one from the floor.

582
01:27:34,606 --> 01:27:35,573
On the right.

583
01:27:57,831 --> 01:28:00,643
This place is really perfect.

584
01:28:22,023 --> 01:28:24,287
This smell is really awful.

585
01:28:45,415 --> 01:28:49,780
<i>Because of the shock,
for 2 days, I couldn't do anything.</i>

586
01:28:56,426 --> 01:28:59,286
<i>Even if I don't do anything
to start with.</i>

587
01:29:11,909 --> 01:29:13,069
<i>What's wrong with me?</i>

588
01:29:20,019 --> 01:29:21,179
<i>It's shaking.</i>

589
01:29:27,326 --> 01:29:29,089
Pizza's End?

590
01:29:54,221 --> 01:29:56,086
How dare you answer me?

591
01:29:56,223 --> 01:29:58,884
I'm notjoking, cut the crap.

592
01:29:59,026 --> 01:30:02,393
A guy like you, I'll cut off
both his hands and feet

593
01:30:02,530 --> 01:30:04,998
to make sashimi.

594
01:30:19,014 --> 01:30:21,001
Bring me some water.

595
01:30:27,223 --> 01:30:28,383
It's me.

596
01:30:31,227 --> 01:30:32,592
Don't hang up.

597
01:30:34,630 --> 01:30:37,394
The weather is dull
and I wasn't in a good mood.

598
01:30:38,634 --> 01:30:40,499
Sorry.

599
01:30:41,738 --> 01:30:44,298
I said I'm sorry, punk!

600
01:30:44,440 --> 01:30:47,103
You're really getting
on my nerves.

601
01:30:48,145 --> 01:30:50,875
You're not even good
at delivering

602
01:30:51,014 --> 01:30:53,881
and who do you think
you're talking to!

603
01:30:54,017 --> 01:30:58,579
I paid your two-weeks salary
you should be grateful.

604
01:30:58,580 --> 01:31:00,223
Are you trying to say
you are hurt?

605
01:31:00,224 --> 01:31:05,492
Well, I am hurt as much as you.
Cut the crap, punk!

606
01:31:05,630 --> 01:31:09,998
I am much more introvert than
you are! Moron!

607
01:31:13,037 --> 01:31:14,939
Excuse me...

608
01:31:14,940 --> 01:31:19,603
The girl who is working at
your place...

609
01:31:19,744 --> 01:31:23,475
Is it her day off today?

610
01:31:26,719 --> 01:31:27,981
Who?

611
01:31:29,722 --> 01:31:31,383
Pale complexion...

612
01:31:33,826 --> 01:31:36,694
Garter belt...

613
01:31:39,231 --> 01:31:40,699
Buttons...

614
01:31:45,338 --> 01:31:47,203
She's my wife.

615
01:31:52,746 --> 01:31:54,706
Just kidding.

616
01:31:57,118 --> 01:31:58,779
She also quit yesterday.

617
01:32:00,221 --> 01:32:02,280
She stopped delivering?

618
01:32:02,924 --> 01:32:05,482
This is really perfect...

619
01:32:12,634 --> 01:32:14,998
The little one said...

620
01:32:16,638 --> 01:32:19,096
she'd never come out again.

621
01:32:19,641 --> 01:32:22,102
You must be all crazy.

622
01:32:25,948 --> 01:32:28,409
She had been working for
some time.

623
01:32:31,221 --> 01:32:32,984
Where does she live?

624
01:32:35,925 --> 01:32:38,681
3 Daizawa, I think.

625
01:32:38,928 --> 01:32:41,431
Don't bother about the pizza.

626
01:32:49,439 --> 01:32:50,907
<i>When a hikikomori</i>

627
01:32:52,342 --> 01:32:54,402
<i>wants to meet a hikikomori</i>

628
01:32:56,046 --> 01:32:57,604
<i>there is only one way.</i>

629
01:34:40,857 --> 01:34:42,358
<i>What a blinding light.</i>

630
01:34:42,359 --> 01:34:45,590
<i>It's so hot.</i>

631
01:34:45,729 --> 01:34:51,895
<i>I hate sweating.</i>

632
01:34:53,136 --> 01:34:55,204
<i>Why did I come out?</i>

633
01:34:56,240 --> 01:35:00,802
<i>Right.</i>

634
01:35:00,945 --> 01:35:03,047
<i>I'm going... Where?</i>

635
01:35:03,048 --> 01:35:05,311
<i>To the left.</i>

636
01:35:05,449 --> 01:35:09,408
<i>The subway station...</i>

637
01:35:09,553 --> 01:35:10,955
<i>No, the bus is better.</i>

638
01:35:10,956 --> 01:35:15,825
<i>3 Daizawa...</i>

639
01:35:16,328 --> 01:35:19,388
<i>Right, I don't have any money.</i>

640
01:35:19,531 --> 01:35:23,491
<i>Nobody must see me.</i>

641
01:35:23,636 --> 01:35:26,037
<i>Where do I have to go?</i>

642
01:35:26,038 --> 01:35:29,007
<i>Yes, of course.</i>

643
01:35:29,141 --> 01:35:32,305
<i>Great.</i>

644
01:35:32,445 --> 01:35:36,609
<i>This...</i>

645
01:35:36,749 --> 01:35:38,910
<i>Passing by Sangenjaya...</i>

646
01:35:39,052 --> 01:35:42,510
<i>Come on...</i>

647
01:35:42,655 --> 01:35:45,216
<i>I can ride this...</i>

648
01:35:45,359 --> 01:35:52,891
<i>I can be there in 30 minutes.</i>

649
01:35:53,033 --> 01:35:56,697
<i>Whatever, Let's go.</i>

650
01:35:56,837 --> 01:36:01,001
<i>Let's walk.</i>

651
01:36:01,141 --> 01:36:05,909
<i>Off we go.</i>

652
01:36:06,748 --> 01:36:09,717
<i>Good. Full steam ahead.</i>

653
01:37:29,536 --> 01:37:30,900
Excuse me. I would...

654
01:39:28,661 --> 01:39:32,120
<i>They all went back in.</i>

655
01:39:40,073 --> 01:39:41,233
<i>All of them.</i>

656
01:39:53,554 --> 01:39:54,714
<i>This man...</i>

657
01:39:57,257 --> 01:40:00,126
<i>I was like him 5 years ago.</i>

658
01:40:02,963 --> 01:40:05,765
<i>For her, it must
have been 10 years...</i>

659
01:40:05,766 --> 01:40:07,325
<i>15 years?</i>

660
01:40:14,276 --> 01:40:16,107
<i>This guy is a rookie.</i>

661
01:40:19,548 --> 01:40:20,708
<i>As for her...</i>

662
01:40:46,577 --> 01:40:47,941
Come out, please.

663
01:40:50,247 --> 01:40:52,511
Quick, come out.

664
01:41:04,062 --> 01:41:06,263
If you don't come out now

665
01:41:06,264 --> 01:41:08,327
you never will.

666
01:41:14,373 --> 01:41:16,637
Listen to me.

667
01:41:16,775 --> 01:41:18,641
Open the door!

668
01:41:18,777 --> 01:41:21,940
At least, tell me your name.

669
01:41:32,658 --> 01:41:34,820
It's collapsing!

670
01:41:35,461 --> 01:41:37,429
It's collapsing!

671
01:41:39,465 --> 01:41:43,129
Come out!

672
01:41:44,771 --> 01:41:48,036
Everybody, come out!

673
01:41:50,377 --> 01:41:52,242
Come out!

674
01:41:55,783 --> 01:41:58,512
What is she waiting for?

675
01:43:29,682 --> 01:43:31,649
Don't go back.

676
01:43:36,757 --> 01:43:38,815
Don't touch me!

677
01:43:41,260 --> 01:43:42,626
Don't go back in.

678
01:44:00,881 --> 01:44:02,144
I pushed it.

679
01:45:16,561 --> 01:45:18,561
It's shaking.

